skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: cookie counter
des:
Let Alexa count for you!

Just say "Cookie Counter, count to seven" and you will her Alexa counting from one to seven.
You can also specify the start number by saying "Cookie Counter, count from four to nine".
